'''Don Henderson''' ([[November 10]], [[1930s|1931]]–[[June 22]], [[1997]]) was an English actor who portrayed [[General]] [[Cassio Tagge]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

He is also known to sci-fi fans for appearing in [[Wikipedia:Doctor Who|Doctor Who]] as the villain Gavrok in the story [[Wikipedia:Delta and the Bannermen|Delta and the Bannermen]] (1987) and in Red Dwarf VII as a Simulant in Beyond a Joke (1997), his final role before his death.

